ftware development experience, exceeding the required 3 years.\\\",\\n  \\\"Demonstrates strong proficiency in Python with several projects; less experience in Java.\\\",\\n  \\\"Possesses hands-on experience with AWS (EC2, S3, Lambda) but no experience with Azure or GCP.\\\",\\n  \\\"Exhibits a solid understanding of data structures and algorithms through academic work and coding challenges.\\\",\\n  \\\"Proficient in MySQL and PostgreSQL, including database design and optimization.\\\",\\n  \\\"Experience in designing and implementing RESTful APIs, showcasing knowledge of API versioning and authentication.\\\",\\n  \\\"Holds a Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, meeting the educational requirement.\\\",\\n  \\\"Evidences strong problem-solving skills through algorithmic project solutions and efficient bug fixes.\\\",\\n  \\\"Demonstrates effective communication skills via leading team code reviews and delivering client presentations.\\\",\\n  \\\"Overall, the candidate is a strong match for the role, particularly in Python, databases, and AWS; Java proficiency is an area for potential growth.\\\"\\n]\\n```\\n\\nTask task2:\\n  Objective: Prepare and send emails (e.g., invitation, follow-up) based on the job details.\\n  Result: ```python\\n[\\n  \\\"Send interview invitation email\\\",\\n  \\\"Send follow-up email after interview\\\",\\n  \\\"Send rejection email if candidate is not selected\\\",\\n  \\\"Send offer email if candidate is selected\\\",\\n  \\\"Send reminder email for interview\\\",\\n  \\\"Send thank you email to the candidate after the interview\\\"\\n]\\n```\\n\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nTask task4:\\n  Objective: Score the candidate's responses from the technical interview.\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nConduct the technical interview using the defined questions and record candidate responses.\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nPlain text\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```python\\n[\\n  \\\"Present coding challenge: Implement a function to reverse a string in Python.\\\",\\n  \\\"Evaluate candidate's problem-solving approach and code efficiency.\\\",\\n  \\\"Ask about their experience with different data structures and algorithms.\\\",\\n  \\\"Inquire about their understanding of database design and optimization.\\\",\\n  \\\"Ask about API design principles, versioning, and authentication methods.\\\",\\n  \\\"Assess their knowledge of cloud computing platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP).\\\",\\n  \\\"Record candidate's code implementation and explanations.\\\",\\n  \\\"Note candidate's communication skills and clarity of thought.\\\",\\n  \\\"Ask about their experience with unit testing and debugging.\\\",\\n  \\\"Evaluate candidate's ability to handle edge cases and error conditions.\\\"\\n]\\n```\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-26T18:03:52.567080\"\n}"}
